{{infobox Chinese|l=Yin Water Pig|kanji=癸亥|romaji=mizunoto i|onyomi=kigai|p=guǐhài|w=kuei-hai|mi=kʷeɪ̯²¹ xaɪ̯|y=gwai2 hoi6|j=gwai2 hoi6|ci=kʷɐi hɐi|mc=kjwɨj ɣəi|oc-bs=kʷeʔ ɢəʔ}}
{{Sexagenary cycle comprehensive}}
'''Yin Water Pig also known as 癸亥''' (mizu no toi, kisui no inoshishi, kigai) is one of the elements of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|六十干支|12=draft|12=draft}}.

It is the 60th (last) combination of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|六十干支|12=draft|12=draft}}, preceded by {{ill|Rinxu|ja|壬戌|12=draft|12=draft}} and followed by {{ill|Koushi|ja|甲子|12=draft|12=draft}}. In the framework of {{ill|Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|ja|陰陽五行思想|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|12=draft|12=draft}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|12=draft|12=draft}} symbol {{ill|Gui|ja|癸|1=Mizunoto (癸)|12=draft|12=draft}} represents yin {{ill|Water|ja|水|12=draft|12=draft}}, and the {{ill|Earthly Branches|ja|十二支|12=draft|12=draft}} symbol {{ill|Pig|ja|亥|1=Pig (zodiac)|lt=Pig (亥)|12=draft|12=draft}} represents yin {{ill|Water|ja|水|12=draft|12=draft}}, forming a harmonious relationship ({{ill|Hiwa|ja|比和|12=draft|12=draft}}).

==Yin Water Pig (癸亥)'s Years==
A year in the {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦|12=draft|12=draft}} that leaves a remainder of 3 when divided by 60 is a {{ill|year|ja|年|12=draft|12=draft}} of {{ill|Kigai|ja|癸亥|12=draft|12=draft}}.
