The {{ill|selected day|ja|選日|1=Senjitsu|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} for {{ill|Kigai|ja|癸亥|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} is the last day of {{ill|Hassen|ja|八専|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.

